<section name="396">
	<p>
		The market square in Marlock City is huge. Armed guards stand around the edge to enforce General Marlock&#8217;s will. Merchants and traders from all over Harkuna hawk their goods in a dozen languages.
	</p>
	<p>
		Items with no purchase price listed are not available locally. The general has imposed a sales tax on all trade; the tax has been included in all the prices listed.
	</p>
